<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abnormal Template Library – Types</title><link>https://scurrra.github.io/atl/docs/types/</link><description>Recent content in Types on Abnormal Template Library</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://scurrra.github.io/atl/docs/types/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Flag</title><link>https://scurrra.github.io/atl/docs/types/flag/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://scurrra.github.io/atl/docs/types/flag/</guid><description>
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;C++ &lt;code&gt;enum class&lt;/code&gt; lacks option composition, so it can&amp;rsquo;t be used directly as flag. &lt;code&gt;abl::flag&lt;/code&gt; is an elegant tool to bring flag functionality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:flex-col hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-4 hx:px-4 hx:border-gray-200 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-red-200 hx:bg-red-100 hx:text-red-900 hx:dark:border-red-200/30 hx:dark:bg-red-900/30 hx:dark:text-red-200"&gt;
